1. When assigning a new project, what can you do to make the learning process easier for a new report?
Solution : B. Establish a second in command whom they can go to with questions

2. Letting your reports do which of the following is an important part of the delegation process?
Solution : A. Experiment and learn from their mistakes

3. What should you do if there is a gap between your expectations and the work completed at a check-in with your report?
Solution : C. Review any missteps and help your employee learn from them
